Dumi Masilela's one million tombstone shock the world A one million tombstone was erected for Dumi Masila after his burial.&nbsp; Dumi's tombstone describes all that he was and all that he believed in.&nbsp; His wife Simphiwe is shattered but she says her soul is at peace because her husband received a very dignified funeral.&nbsp; I wish I could talk to him one last time and ask for his opinion on the tombstone as we always made decisions together.&nbsp; How do I now move on after leaving my husband at a place where I'll never be able to sleep next to and share my thoughts with .